According to U.S. President Barack Obama , we are dealing with a massive and potentially unprecedented environmental disaster .
While the leak is extremely serious , and Obama s words may ultimately ring true , the leak is -LRB- as yet -RRB- not one of the top 50 biggest oil spillages from either oil rigs or tankers in historical perspective : cents Some 7 - 10 , 000 tonnes of oil are so far estimated to have leaked into the Gulf of Mexico from Deepwater Horizon .
