The largest ever off - shore leakage of oil occurred in <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DATE" value="1979">1979</TIMEX3> in the Ixtoc-1 spillage when an estimated 476,000 tonnes of oil polluted the Gulf of Mexico -LRB- Bay of Campeche -RRB- .
